     H            Y.
     *------------------------------------------------------
     *  ANDROID ORDER PROCESSED DATE & TIME
     *
     * TCHK1 07/12/06 CREATE(COPY FROM AB#R0Y)
     *------------------------------------------------------
     FAB#PPCT IF  E           K        DISK
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  80
     C                     PARM           P@TIME  60
      *
     C           K#KEY     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@KWD1  8
     C                     KFLD           K@KWD2  8
      *
     C                     MOVEL'ANDROID' K@KWD1    P
     C                     MOVEL'862GNTRN'K@KWD2    P
      *
     C           K#KEY     CHAINAB#PPCT              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     P@DATE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     P@TIME
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDCTNBR1    P@DATE
     C                     Z-ADDCTNBR2    P@TIME
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
